Class RequestConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.RequestConfig
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AmazonWebServiceRequestAdapter

    public abstract class RequestConfig
extends Object
    Generic representation of request level configuration. The customer interface for specifying request level configuration is a base request class with configuration methods.
